videos.description: Nate Johnson comes up with the steal and speeds down the court to get an easy layup and cap the Xavier fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Nate Johnson gets the steal and bucket for Xavier) 2020/12/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nate Johnson gets the steal and bucket for Xavier

videos.description: With under a minute to go before halftime, Colby Johnson comes up with the steal and gets the ball to Zach Freemantle to stuff down a dunk to cap the Xavier fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Xavier's Freemantle dunks on fast break) 2020/12/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Xavier's Freemantle dunks on fast break

videos.description: Nate Johnson catches fire from behind the arc in the corner as he makes two 3-pointers from the same spot on consecutive possessions for Xavier.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Xavier's Johnson drills two 3s in a row from the same spot) 2020/12/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Xavier's Johnson drills two 3s in a row from the same spot
